author: rhuijben
msg: Provide a nicer api to determine which conflicts are stored in a conflict
skel to avoid using error codes for common code paths.
Prepare some (currently disabled) tree conflict install code.
(conflict__read_location): Use a const skel and apr_pstrmemdup.
(svn_wc__conflict_read_info): Use a const skel in a few places. Add output
svn_wc__conflict_read_prop_conflict): Use a const skel and apr_pstrmemdup.
(svn_wc__conflict_create_markers): Use a read_info call to determine conflict
(svn_wc__conflict_invoke_resolver): Use a read_info call to determine conflict
(mark_conflict): Use read_info as base data. Remove some commented code
that will later be enabled to create tree conflicts.
